  "bio_html": "Aakash is currently a doctoral student advised by Dr <a href=\"https://warwick.ac.uk/fac/sci/dcs/people/fayyaz_minhas/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Fayyaz ul Amir Afsar Minhas</a> at the <a href=\"https://warwick.ac.uk/fac/cross_fac/tia/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tissue Image Analytics Centre (TIA) Centre</a>, under the School of Computer Science at the University of Warwick. Aakash's work focuses on developing machine-learning methods for computational pathology, particularly analysing whole-slide histopathology images to discover clinically relevant biomarkers and improve disease characterisation, as part of a joint industry-academia project with <a href=\"https://www.gsk.com/en-gb/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">GSK</a>. Previously, Aakash completed a MSc in Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning from the University of Birmingham and a PgD and BSc in Computer Science from Ashoka University.",
